column5: Cute Kitty! Now, here's what you need to do... Grab you flippin stick, tie on a little pouch with catnip and practise your flippin techniques this winter on that little one! You'll both enjoy the cold weather a little more! HH
Yep, got the ice-fishing rod in mind lol
Love the one little "tan" paw...adorable  blyght
Love that second picture, the look is priceless...enjoy, and watch your toes  Maureen
Wrong season to get a kitty it will be to big to use for bait by Muskie season....... Guess you are stuck with a cute kitten this time.  Art
that's the devil i tell ya, he's lookin thru my soul

The look in its eyes in the second picture is the same one it will have when the Musky is closing in on it!! Good idea getting it early.  Should be nice and plump by next June..... Seriously nice kitten.  Always lots of fun.
